name: Unidentified_Naboo_child
content:
This Human female was present at the victory parade in Theed following the Invasion of Naboo.
This character was played by Madison Lloyd, younger sister of Jake Lloyd, and was mentioned as Ellie in Call Sheets of Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. In an interview in Star Wars Insider 39, Jake Lloyd revealed this character was called Princess Ellie. However, this name has never appeared in any canon source, and Leland Chee has stated that the character does not have an official name.
